When GNSS signal is good, GNSS can be used for accurate positioning; The GNSS signal is poor. When the lighting conditions meet the requirements of the intelligent vision system,the intelligent vision system is used for positioning. If both GNSS signal and visual assistant positioning fail, it will automatically switch to mode A and be manually controlled by a professional pilot.

When BDS signal is good, BDS can be used for accurate positioning; The BDS signal is poor. When the lighting conditions meet the requirements of the intelligent vision system,the intelligent vision system is used for positioning. If both BDS signal and visual assistant positioning fail, it will automatically switch to mode A and be manually controlled by a professional pilot.

S mode is an enhanced mode under P mode. In this mode, the aircraft performance is improved, and GNSS and lower visual perception positioning work normally. In this mode, the obstacle avoidance system is closed, and the aircraft cannot avoid obstacles by itself
